\id 1CO  
\h 1 Corinth 
\toc1 Corinth Mite Henga Paul Lekhathot Khatna 
\toc2 1 Corinth 
\toc3 1 Crth 
\mt1 CORINTH  
\mt2 MITE HENGA  
\mt3 PAUL LEKHATHOT KHATNA  
\is1 Ngailutna sodoh tei ding lunggon neiyin  
\is1 Houbung boina neipet a dinga chihna thuseiho!  
\is1 1 Corinth lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Corinth Houbung a kiboina, kibung khenna, kinahna, anaum hin Christian ho lhagao thua alhahsamnau akimudoh in ahi. Tulai dinmun to kitoh boinaho-Court ahilouleh Haosa kom'a kiheh, jinei kisuhlouna, kida chule lhagao thilpeh thudol'a kiboina umho thudol akiseiyin chule tulai Houbungin chutobang phat teng, iti ding ham ti thun Solchah Paul in hilna aneiyin ahi. Paul in Pathen chate ho chu chonna thenga chon ding, Lhagao Theng chenna ahiu \xt 1 Crth 3:16; 1 Crth 6:19\xt*, lunghanna khel'a kiphalam geh cha a um, lungkham khel'a lungnema Pakai Jesu a chonphatna alahtah diu thudol'a hilna anei ahi. Solchah Paul in kithangthipna ho, kiletsahna ho hin Christian kipumkhatna le kingailutna adal-e ti aseiyin ahi.  
\ip Hijeh chun hiche lekhathot hi simjom jinga pha ahi. Hiche lekhabu nasim'a kon'a nangma hinkho kikhol chilna neiya hoilai pen chu na kisuhdih ding ham, ti naki mudoh thei ding ahi.  
\is1 Lekhathot jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Hiche lekhabu jihpa hi Solchah Paul ahi. Aman hiche lekhabu hi AD 54 ahilouleh AD 55 kum'a ajih hidin ginchat ahi.  
\is1 Koi henga ajih ham?  
\ip Solchah Paul in Corinth kiti kiveina khopia cheng Greece gamsunga Gentile pengthah ho henga ajih ahi. Solchah Paul in Corinth Houbung hi ana phudoh jou kum ni, kum thum jouvin boina phabep in ahin phatai. Houbunga kitomona, kibung khenna, lhagaova louchalna, jinei kisuhlouna, penthah chanpi alam louva bolna, lhagao thilpeh mankhelna, lhagaova pilhin theilouna ho jeh a boina jatchom chom umho suhthip le lhagaova kiledohsahna ding deina a hiche lekhathot hi anajih ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Lemna thu  
\p
\v 1 Hiche lekhathot hi Pathen lung cham'a kilhengdoh Jesu Christa solchah Paul le isopiu Sosthenes a kon ahi.  
\v 2 Keiman Pathen houbung Corinth a um nangho Pathen'in amitheng te hi dinga akouho henga kahin sut ahi. Aman Christa Jesu jal'a athenga nasem'u ahi, mun jousea Christian ho jouse, I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa, amaho le eiho dinga Pakai, min hin kouho jouse abolna banga.\x + \xo 1:2 \xt Act 18:1\x*  
\v 3 I-Pau Pathen le Pakai Jesu Christa chun nangho lungset le cham lungmon napeu hen.   
\s1 Corinth'a Lhagao thilpeh ho  
\p
\v 4 Nangho tua hi Christa Jesu a nahi jalun chule lungsetna thilpeh napeh jalun keiman ka Pathen chu ka thangvah jingin ahi.  
\v 5 Ama a konna na houbung uhi Pathen'in imalam jousea nahaosah u ahin, thusei thepna le hetthemna jouse hi naneiyu ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche hin keiman Christa chung thu ka seipeh uhi adih e ti aphotchen ahi.  
\v 7 Nanghon tua lhagao thilpeh tintang na ngaichat ho'u chu I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa hungkitna ding kinem'a ngah a nahi jeh uva naneiyu ahitai.  
\v 8 Aman achaina geiya nahatsah uva, I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa ahung niteng nolnabei hinkho naman theina dingu ahi.  
\v 9 Pathen hi tahsan umtah ahina jal'a Aman abol dinga asei chu thon louhel a ahinbol ding ahin, chule Ama chun Achapa Pakai Jesu a chan neikhom dinga na ngeh u ahitai.   
\s1 Loitum sem chonset ahi  
\p
\v 10 Kasopi deitahte, I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa thuneina a kangeh nom nau chu nangho khat le khat kilungtoh tah in umun. Houbunga kibung khenna umhih hen. Chusang'in lungkhat kisauvin, lunggel le lungtup kithakhat hiuvin.  
\v 11 Ajeh chu kasopi deitahte, Chloe insung mite phabep in kitohmoa naum u thu chu kajah a ahung seiyuve.  
\v 12 Nangho lah a mi phabep in, “Keima Paul nungjui kahi,” abangkhat loiyin, “Apollos nung kajuiye,” ahilouleh, “Peter nungjui kahi,” ahilouleh “Christa bou kajui ahi,” natiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 1:12 \xt Act 18:24\x*  
\v 13 Christa chu loituma achom cheh a nakhen'u hitam? Keima Paul hi nangho dinga kikhenbeh a kahim? Nalah uva Paul min'a baptize kibol naum uvem? Naum hih nauve!  
\v 14 Nalah uva Crispus le Gaius tailou khatcha baptize kana bollou jeh in Pathen ka thangvah e.\x + \xo 1:14 \xt Act 18:8; \xt Act 19:29; Rm 16:23\x*  
\v 15 Ajeh iham itileh tua hi koima chan kamin'in baptize einabol'e eiti theilou dingu ahitai.  
\v 16 (Oh ahinai, keiman Stephenas insung pumpi jong chu baptize kanabol nai, ahinlah koima dang baptize kabolbe kahepoi).\x + \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Crth 16:15\x*  
\v 17 Ajeh chu Christan keima baptize bol le dinga eisol ahipoi, Kipana Thupha seiphong le dinga bou eisol ahi. Christa thingpel chun athaneina aman louna dinga chihna thudol asei kahilou ahi.   
\s1 Pathen thahatna le chihna Christa  
\p
\v 18 Ajeh chu thingpel thu hi mahthahna lam mano ho dinga ngol hoitah thu ahi. Hinlah eiho huhhingna chang ho dinga Pathen thahatna ahi.  
\v 19 Pathen Thubun aseima bangin, “Keiman miching ho chihna chu kasuhbei ding, chule milungching chihna chu imacha hilouva kakoi ding ahi” ati.\x + \xo 1:19 \xt Isa 29:14\x*  
\v 20 Hiti ahijeh chun, chihgilna neiho, lekhathem ho, chule vannoi lungthim themna a minelkal hat ho iti tauvintem? Pathen'in hiche vannoi chihna chu angola amu ahi bouve.\x + \xo 1:20 \xt Job 12:17; Isa 19:12; 33:18; \xt Isa 44:25\x*  
\v 21 Pathen'in achihna a vannoiyin mihem chihnaa Ama ahetdoh lou dingu ahi ti amu jeh a, angol ho thusei banga ka thuseiyu hin atahsan ho ahuhhingna dinga amanchah ahi.  
\v 22 Van'a konna melchihna thum Judah nam mite dinga hichu ngol thu ahin, chule Greek mite, mihem chihnaa hol ho dinga jong ngol thubuh ahi.  
\v 23 Hitia hi keihon Christa kikhetbeh thu kaseiyu hi Judah nam mite lunghan kondohna ahung hin chule chidang namdang hon panna bei thu kisei ahi bouve, atiuvin ahi.  
\v 24 Hinlah Pathen'in huhhing dinga akou ho dingin vang, Judah mi hihen chidang namdang hijongleh, Christa chu Pathen thahatna le Pathen chihna ahigel e.  
\v 25 Hiche Pathen'in ngol tah a tohgon anei hi mihem achingpen tohgon sangin jong achingjon chule Pathen thalhahsamna chu mihem thahatna pen sangin jong ahatjo nalaiye.   
\ms1 Pakai jenga bou loupina  
\p
\v 26 Kasopi deitahte ho geldoh temun, Pathen'in nanakou pet u chun hiche vannoi lamdol a aching'ah ahilouleh athaneiyah ahilouleh ahaovah naum pouve.  
\v 27 Chusangin, vannoiyin angol'a agel ho'u chu Pathen'in ching kisaho jachatsahna dinga alhendoh ahi. Chule Aman thaneilou ho jong chu thanei tah a kigel ho jachatsahna a alhendoh ahi.  
\v 28 Pathen'in hiche vannoiyin anahsahmo ho, imacha louva agel ho, chu alhendoh a, vannoiyin thupitah a agel ho imacha hilou sosah dinga manchah dinga alhendoh ahi.  
\v 29 Akhkonna keiya, koimacha Pathen angsunga akiletsah hoitho umlouna ding ahi.  
\v 30 Pathen'in Christa Jesu toh nagop khomu ahitai. Iphatchompina ding uva Pathen'in chihna tahbeh chu Ama ahisah ahitai. Christan eiho Pathen toh isuhchamu ahitah jeh in, Aman eiho athenga chule athengsel a eisem uva, chule chonset a konna eilha ongtholu ahitai.  
\v 31 Hiche jeh a chu Pathen Thubun asei, “Nangma nakison noma ahileh Pakai chungthua bou kisongin,” ati ahi.\x + \xo 1:31 \xt Jeremiah 9:24\x*   
\c 2  
\s1 Thingpel'a kikhetbeh Christa  
\p
\v 1 Sopite ho, keima naheng uva kahung masat chun Pathen'in guhthima athilgon kasei phongna dingah thugiltah ho le ngainom nom chihguh thuseina ho kamangchapoi.  
\v 2 Ijeh ham itileh keima nangho toh kana umkhom pet chun, thil dang jouse suhmila, thingpela kikhenbeh Jesu Christa thubou chu kagel dinga kalung gon ahitai.  
\v 3 Thalhom tah in naheng uvah kichageu le kithing pumin kana hungin ahi.\x + \xo 2:3 \xt Act 18:9\x*  
\v 4 Chule kathupoh le ka thusei phong chu hetbai lamtah ahi. Chingkeo leh ngehtuntun'a thuseina neilouvin Lhagao Theng thahatna bou kana songin ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche kabol hi nang hon mihem chihna chu tahsan louva Pathen thahatna na tahsan johna ding uva kabol ahi.   
\s1 Lhagao chihna  
\p
\v 6 Hijongleh keima apilhingsa tahsan ho lah a kaum tengleh, keiman chihna thu panin kaseiyin, hiche vannoiya chihna tobang ahilouleh chomkah louva kisumilji vannoi vaipohoa tobangin kaseipoi.  
\v 7 Ahipoi, keihon chihna thu kaseiyu hi Pathen thuguh ana kiselguh chu ahi–akiselguh atil a kiphongdoh khaloulai, vannoi kibulphudoh masanga eiho iloupina diuva atohgon ana umsa chu ahi.  
\v 8 Hinlah hiche vannoi vaipoten ahethei hihbeh uve, hetaveleu, ama hon loupi Pakai chu thingpel a akhetbeh louhel dingu ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche chu ahi Pathen Lekhabun, “Koima mit nin amulou le koima nakolin ajah khahlou chule koima lunga jong kondoh khalou Pathen'in Ama ngailu ho dinga agonsa ahi” tia asei chu.\x + \xo 2:9 \xt Isa 64:4\x*  
\v 10 Hinlah eiho hengah Pathen'in hiche ho chu a-Lhagaovin eihil tauvin ahi. Ijeh inem itileh Lhagaovin ijakai akholdoh a chule Pathen thuguh ho chu eivetsah u ahitai.  
\v 11 Koiman mikhat lunggel ahepoi, amipa lhagao bouvin akihet ahi, chule koiman Pathen lunggel ahepoi, Pathen Lhagao bouvin ahet ahi.  
\v 12 Chule eihon Pathen Lhagao ikisan tauve (vannoi lhagao ahipoi), hijeh a chu Pathen'in manbeiya eipeh u thil kidangtah ho chu ihet theiyu ahi.  
\v 13 Keihon hiche ho ka seipeh uhi, mihem chihna thuchengho mang'ah kahi pouve. Chusangin, Lhagaovin eipeh u thucheng kamang chauve, Lhagao thutah ho chu Lhagao thuchenga ka hilchet jiu ahi.  
\v 14 Hinlah Lhagao lam gellou ho chun Pathen Lhagaova konna thudih ho chu asang thei pouve. Ama hon ngolthua agel jeh uvin ahethei hihbeh uve, ijeh inem itileh lhagao lam gelkhoh ho bouvin Lhagao sei chu ahe theiye.  
\v 15 Lhagao lam gel hon ima jouse aman lutdan ageldoh theiyun, hinlah amaho tah chu koiman amanlut dan'u geldohna anei thei pouve.  
\v 16 Ijeh inem itileh, “Koiham Pakai lung ngaito hea, koiham Ama hiltheina geiya hetna neiya chu?” Hinlah eihon hiche ho jouse hi ihe tauve, ajeh chu eihon Christa lunggel chu ihetauve.\x + \xo 2:16 \xt Isa 40:13\x*   
\c 3  
\s1 Loitum sem hi tahsalam chonna ahi  
\p
\v 1 Sopite, keima nangho toh kaum khom pet in Lhagao miho lah a thusei tobangin naheng uva thu kasei theipoi. Keiman nangho jah a vannoi mite tobanga thusei dingin ahilouleh Christian hinkhoa chapang neocha ho lah a thuseiya kasei dingin naum uve.  
\v 2 Keiman nangho bongnoiya kavah uva, an-ham'a kavah louding nahiuve, ajeh chu nangho ahamjep nehna dingin nahi thei hih laiyuve.\x + \xo 3:2 \xt Heb 5:12,13\x*  
\v 3 Ijeh inem itileh nangho na chonset nomnau lunggel in nathujo nalaiyuve. Nangho naki thangsetto nalaiyun chule khat le khat kinah le kisaovin naum uve. Hichun nangho na chonset nau lungchangin nathunun nahlaiyu aphotchet hilou ham? Nangho vannoi mite hin'a hing nalai nahilou uham?  
\v 4 Nangho lah a khat in, “Keima Paul nungjui kahi”, atia chule achom dang khat in, “Keiman Apollos nung kajui ahi” atileh nangho vannoi mite chon'a chon'ah nahiu hilou ham?\x + \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Crth 1:12\x*   
\s1 Twichap, Anatoh, Gihna  
\p
\v 5 Adih a sei dingin, Apollos chu koi hiya, Paul chu koi ham? Keini hi Kipana Thupha na tahsan na ding uva Pathen lhacha natong kahi lhonin, Pakaiyin eingansena lhon toh kitoh a kahil lhon ahi.  
\v 6 Keiman na lungsung uva muchi katulut ahin, Apollos chun atwi achap a chule Pathen chu akhansah a pang ahi bouve.\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Act 18:4-11; \xt Act 18:24-28\x*  
\v 7 Koi chu aphut a panga, ahilouleh atwichap koiham ti chu akhohjo dehpoi. Akhohjopen chu Pathen akhansahpa chu ahi.  
\v 8 Aphut a panga le atwichap a panga chun lunggon thakhat aneigel lhon ahi. Chule anatoh gut jal lhon'a chu kipaman amu lhon ding ahi.  
\v 9 Ajeh iham itileh keini Pathen natong kahi lhonin chule nangho Pathen lou nahiuvin, Pathen In nahiuve.  
\v 10 Pathen lungsetna kachan jal'a keiman insa themtah tobanga abul kaphudoh ahitai. Tua hi midangin achunga chu asah u ahi. Hinlah hiche khombul chunga sadoh a pangho chun ching theitah a asah dingu ahi.  
\v 11 Keihon abul kaphudohsau kalval koiman adang phut theilou ding ahiuve, hiche abul chu Jesu Christa ahi.  
\v 12 Koi hijongleh hiche abula saa chun amanchah nom nom amanchah thei ahi-Sana, dangka, songmantam, thing, bi ahilouleh pol amanchah thei ahi.  
\v 13 Hinlah thutan nikho lechun itobanga in asah ahi kipatep ding ahi. Mikhat natoh chu ichan'a luaham ti avetsah ding ahi.  
\v 14 Natoh chu aumdena ahileh, hiche insa achun tohphat man akisan ding ahi.  
\v 15 Hinlah natoh chu meiyin akahvam'a ahileh insa'a pang chu haman'a mang ding ahitai. A insa'a chu huhhing hinantin, ahin ama chu meikahna a konna hung sohcha tobang bep hi ding ahi.  
\v 16 Nangho na boncha uva kigoma Pathen Hou-In nahiuva chule Pathen Lhagao chu nanghoa chenga ahi chu helou nahiuvem?\x + \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Crth 6:19; 2 Crth 6:16\x*  
\v 17 Koi hileh hiche Hou-In sumanga chu Pathen'in asuhmang ding ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen Hou-In chu thenga ahin, chule nangho hiche Hou-In chu nahiuve.   
\s1 Vannoi chihna nungsun un  
\p
\v 18 Nanghon kijoulhepna kingahdoh uvin. Nangho tulai vannoi leiset lamdol'a chinga kigel'a nahiu leh chingtah beh nahina ding uva angol nahiu angaiye.  
\v 19 Ajeh iham itileh hiche vannoi chihna hi Pathen a dinga angol ahi. Pathen Lekhabu thun asei dungjuiya, “Aman michingho chu achihnau thangkol'a a-osah in,”\x + \xo 3:19 \xt Job 5:13\x*  
\v 20 chule “Pakaiyin miching ho lunggel ahen, imacha phatchomna umlou ahi ahei” kiti ahi.\x + \xo 3:20 \xt Labu 94:11\x*  
\v 21 “Hiti ahijeh chun lamkai mihem khat juijeh in hoitho hih in. Ijeh inem itileh ijakai nanghoa ahi.  
\v 22 Paul ahilouleh Apollos ahilouleh Peter ahilouleh vannoi ahilouleh hinna le thina tua le khonunga ding hijongleh, aboncha nanghoa ahi,  
\v 23 chule nangho Christaa nahiuvin, chule Christa chu Pathen a ahi.”   
\c 4  
\s1 Pathen thuguh chingtup  
\p
\v 1 Hijeh chun Apollos le keima hi, Pakai lhacha Pathen thu ki-imho phongdoh a ngansena changa kahi lhon bouve tin neigel jouvin.  
\v 2 Hichea avetup a ngansena chang mi chu tahsan umtah mi ahi angaiye.  
\v 3 Hinlah keima dingin nang hon ahilouleh mi koiham khat touvin eikholtoh ding chu thil thupin kagelpoi. Keima chung chang thua kakikhol ding jong ahipoi.  
\v 4 Keiman ase le apha kahetna thu akicheh in, hinlah hichu keima kadih monge tina ahipoi. Keima chung thu kholtoh ding le gellhahna nei dinga chu Pakai Ama tah ahi.  
\v 5 Hiti ahijeh chun Pakai ahung phat masangin koima chung thu tanlhah jeng na neihih un. Ajeh chu Aman guhthima muthim lah a ibol jouseu chu vah a akilahdoh sah ding chule ichan cheh diu ilunggon hou chu ahin tahlang ding ahiye. Chuphat leh Pathen'in amichang cheh a vahchoina dinga lom ahina uva apeh cheh dingu ahi.   
\ms1 Christa jal'a angol  
\p
\v 6 Sopi deitahte, keiman kaseisa thua hin avetsahnan, keima tah le Apollos to kani lhonin kana hil tauvin ahi. Keiman Pathen Thubua konna kalahdoh a kahinsei chu phatah in lunga ngaitona neileu chun midang mosahna dinga nalamkaiyu khat kiletsah hoithopia naum louhel dingu ahi.  
\v 7 Hitobang loma dinga chu kon thutan theina napeh u hintem? Pathen pehlou ipi naneiyu umem? Chule nanei jouseu chu Pathen a kon ahi, iti dana thilpeh chang hilou tobanga kiletsah hoithona neiya nahiu ham?  
\v 8 Nanghon na ngaichat chan neiyin nakigelun ahi. Nangho aning lhingin nakigelun ahi. Keiho pang louva Pathen Lenggama vaipopa nahiuve! Vaipoa pang hitaleu chun kati lheh in ahi, chuti hen lang hileh nangho toh vaipo khom kahi diu ahitai.  
\v 9 Chusangin, Pathen'in keiho hi vannoi pumpia miho le vantil ho vetnom hi ding a galjo nunga sohchang gal hinga kikai, tha dinga gonsa tobang bep a solchah a eikoiyu hi dingin kagel in ahi.  
\v 10 Christaa kaki lhandoh nau hi angola toh kabang uve, hinlah nangho hi Christa a chingtah in naki seiyun ahi! Keiho hi kalhasamun, hinlah nangho nathanei lheh jengun ahi! Nangho jabol nachang uvin, hinlah keiho hi isahlou tah in eikibol uvin ahi.  
\v 11 Tujeng jong hin keiho gilkel le dangchah thoh in kavah leuvin, chule kitomlumna ding pon jong kanei pouve. Keiho hi eikivo lhoiyun, chule gena in kanei pouve.  
\v 12 Keihon thachol tah in kakihinsona ding uvin kakhut tah un na katong gimun ahi. Eigaosap hou phatthei kaboh uve. Alam louva eibol nauva kakido hat un ahi.\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Act 18:3\x*  
\v 13 Keiho chungthua thuse aseina uva lungneng tah in katao tho uvin ahi. Ahivangin keiho hi vannoiya deimon kaumun, tugei hin paiyin kaum nalaiyui.   
\s1 Paul'in mipa lungput aput  
\p
\v 14 Keiman hiche kajih hi nangho jachat sahna ding kagon ahipon, ka-it tah chate hina a kahil chah joh u nahibou uve.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu nang hon Christa thu nahil thei uvah mi sangsom nei jonglehu chun, nang hon Lhagao lama pa khat bou naneiyu ahi. Ajeh chu keiman nangho henga Kipana Thupha kahung seiphong ahitah jeh in nangho dinga keima hi Christa Jesu a napau kahung hi ahitai.  
\v 16 Hiti ahijeh chun keima umchan thouvin kati ahi.\x + \xo 4:16 \xt 1 Crth 11:1; Philp 3:17\x*  
\v 17 Chule keiman Pakaiya kacha ngaitah le tahsan umtah Timothy hi kahinsol ahitai. Ama hin keiman Christa Jesu chu iti kajui ahi; houbung kachena jouse ho kahilna banga chu nangho avel'a nagel dohsah kit dingu ahiye.  
\v 18 Keiman kahung vilkit tah louding gel'a na umjeh uvin, mi phabep nalah uva alouchal naum tauve.  
\v 19 Hinlah keima kahunga chule gangtah a Pakaiyin eiphalpeh ahileh hiche kihisah tah a thuseiya um ho hi atho thu'u hiya ham ahilouleh Pathen thahat nei hiuvem ti kholdoh nange.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu Pathen Lenggam hi thua seitho seh seh chu ahipoi, hichu Pathen thahatna a hin joh chu ahiye.  
\v 21 Hoijoh nakilhen dingu ham? Keima mol kichoiya gotna pedinga naheng uva kahung ding ham? Ahilouleh ngailutna le lungnenga kahung ding ham?   
\c 5  
\s1 Jonthanhoi in houbung asuhboh  
\p
\v 1 Nalah uva jonthanhoi bola aum'e tithu kajah vang'in katahsan tahbeh theipoi. Hitobang hi milim houho jengin jong abolji pouve. Na houbung sung uvah mikhat in anuno toh chonsetna hinkho amang lhon'e ti eikiseipeh in ahi.\x + \xo 5:1 \xt Danbu Ni Na 22:30\x*  
\v 2 Nangho tah nakiletsah uvin, hinlah nangho hi lungkham le jahchatah a lunghem ding joh nahiuve. Chule hiche mipa chu nakiloikhom nauva konna napaidoh jeng dingu ahi.  
\v 3 Keima tah in nangho na umpi hih u jonglehng, Lhagaova keiman kaumpi nahiuve. Chule aum tobangin, hiche mipa chu achungthu keiman,  
\v 4 Pakai Jesu min'in katan chaitai. Nangho houbung mipi chu nakihou dingu ahi. Keima nangho toh lhagaova kauma chule hitia chu I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa thaneina hi ding ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche mipa chu na nodoh uva chule atahsa lungngaichat chonna chu suhmanga aumna dinga Satan khut a na pehdoh dingu ahi chule ama chu Pakai hung kile nikho teng huhdoh a aumna ding ahi.  
\v 6 Hichung chang thua nahoitho nau hi hoise tah ahi. Hiche chonsetna hi chol them chakhat in changbong kidekot apum changa amonsah soh tobang hilou ham?\x + \xo 5:6 \xt Gal 5:9\x*  
\v 7 Nalah uva kon'in hiche migiloupa chol tobang chu paidoh un. Chutengleh nangho nahinau monga chu changbong lumthah chol kisolou tobang chu nahi dingu ahi. Christa Kalchuh Kut satha khel'a eiho dinga hung kikatdoh a ahitai.\x + \xo 5:7 \xt Potdohbu 12:5\x*  
\v 8 Hiti chun, eihon changlhahlui gitlouna le phatlouna pumin Kut chu bol louvin, ahin changlhah thah mangchan lungdih pun chule thutah in golnop chu bol uhite.\x + \xo 5:8 \xt Potdohbu 13:7; Danbu Ni Na 16:3\x*   
\s1 Jonthanhoi bol ho achungthu tan ding  
\p
\v 9 Masanga nakom uva dinga lekha kahin jih a chu nangho jon lungpua chonse nom jing ho toh kivop hih un tia kana seipeh nahiu ahitai.  
\v 10 Hinlah keiman atahsanlou ho jonlungpua chonse nom jingho, ahilouleh michipse, ahilouleh miho lhemlha a, semthu milimho hou ho thudol kasei ahipoi. Achuti louva ahileh hiche vannoiya hitobang miho a konna kikangse dia vannoi hi na dalhah diu ngaikha ding ahi.  
\v 11 Ken kasei hi tahsan cha kahi tia ahia jonlungpua chonse nom jinga, ahilouleh michipse hia, ahilouleh semthu milimho hou ahia, ahilouleh miseise hat ahia, ahilouleh julop ahia, mi duhabol ahia ahileh, hitobanga chon hotoh kivop hih un. Hitobang miho to chun anjong nekhom hih un katina ahi.  
\v 12 Polama mi thutan ding kakin ahipoi, hinla houbung sunga uma chonset bol ho chung thu natan diu nakin u ahi.\x + \xo 5:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 13:5; 17:7\x*  
\v 13 Pathen'in polamaho thu atan ding ahi, hinla Pathen thubun asei bangin, “Nalah uva migilou chu paidoh un,” ati.   
\c 6  
\s1 Sopiho hehset louding  
\p
\v 1 Nangho lah a atahsan khat in michom atahsan khattoh kinahna aneiya ahileh, itiloma ngam nahiuva atahsan dang ho kom'a suhchet ding golouva, leilam kihehna mun'a gakiheh a nahiuvem?  
\v 2 Nikhat le vannoi thutan'a ihung pan dingu geldoh louva nahiuvem? Chule vannoi thutan'a napan dingu ahileh, hiche thil neocha hoa hi nangma ho tah in gellhahna nanei theilou uham?  
\v 3 Vantil ho thu ihintan dingu geldoh loubeh a nahiuvem? Hitia hi nangho tah in tu hinkhoa kinahna chu suhchamna ding na gelthei diu adoltah ahije.  
\v 4 Hitobang thudol'a dan dungjuiya kinahna nanei uva ahileh itidan'a houbungin ija agellou beh polam mi thutanho kom'a chea nahiuvem?  
\v 5 Hiche keiman kasei hi nangho jachatsahna dinga kati ahi. Hiche chung changa lung gellhah theina pea houbungho jouse lah a jong koima naum lou u hitam?  
\v 6 Hinlah chutia bol louva, atahsan khat in atahsan michom khat–atahsanlou ho masangtah a aheh thei jeng hi!  
\v 7 Hitobang chan geiya khat in khat dan pan'a kihehna nanei uhi nangho kijumsoa nahiuve. Athem moa kahitai tia nanoplhah uva chule hitia chu na ngahdoh jengleu itia ham? Nangmatah chu duha kibol khum joh nahimo uham?  
\v 8 Chusangin, nangho tah thil dihlou bol in napang uvin chule na tahsan kibahpiho najoulhep uve.  
\v 9 Thil dihlou bol ho chun Pathen Lenggam alo lou dingu ahi ti hi nahetdoh lou u ham? Nangho tah kingolbol hih uvin. Ahinlah jonlungpua chonsenom jing ho, ahilouleh pasal kijoh ho, ahilouleh pasal leh pasal jongho,  
\v 10 ahilouleh aguchaho, ahilouleh michipseho, ahilouleh jukhamho, miseiseho, ahilouleh miduhabol ho hitobang bol mi chu khatcha jong Pathen Lenggama lutlouhel dingu ahi.  
\v 11 Nangho lah a phabep hitobang chu nanahiuve. Hinla tua hi nangho angima nahi tauvin, athenga kisem nahi tauvin, Pakai Jesu Christa min pan'a chule Lhagao Theng jal'a Pathen to kilunglhaiya nahi tauve.   
\s1 Tahsa le lhagaova Pathen loupisah ding  
\p
\v 12 Nanghon, “Keiman ipi hijongleh kabol theina dinga eiki phatsah peh ahi,” natiuve-hinlah nangho dingin ima jouse aphadeh a ahipoi. Chule ipi hijongleh keiman kabol thei dingin eikiphatsah jongleh imacha soh in pang hih inge.\x + \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Crth 10:23\x*  
\v 13 Nanghon, “An hi gilpi dinga chule gilpi hi an dinga kisema ahi,” natiuve. (Hichu adih e, hinla Pathen'in nikhat leh ania ahin suhmang ding ahi). Hinla nang hon, itahsau hi ihinau jkonna le thenlouna dinga kisema ahi nati thei pouve. Akopgoma Pakai dinga kisema ahin, chule Pakaiyin itahsa dingu agelkhoh e.  
\v 14 Chule Pathen'in athaneina a I-Pakaiyu thinaa konna akaithou tobanga itahsau hi akaithou ding ahi.  
\v 15 Natahsau chu Christa tibah hitha a ahitai ti hetahbeh lou nahiuvem? Mikhat in atahsa, Christa tibah chu alah a chule noti toh agopkhom tha ding chu angai ham? Angai ahipoi.  
\v 16 Chule pasal khat chu notinu toh kijopmat henlang hileh, amanu chuto amapa chu tipum khat hitalou ding ham? Ajeh iham itileh Pathen Lekhabun, “Anilhon'a chu tipum khat a kigoma ahitai” ati.\x + \xo 6:16 \xt Semtilbu 2:24\x*  
\v 17 Hinlah Pakaiya kijopmat mi chu Ama chutoh lhagao khat ahitai.  
\v 18 Jon lungputna chonsetna a kon'in jamdoh un! Hitobang loma atahsa sukha chonset dang aumpoi. Ajeh iham itileh jonthanhoi lungput hi natahsa douna chonset ahi.  
\v 19 Nasung uva chenga chule Pathen'in nangho napeh u natahsau hi Pathen Lhagao Theng chenna Hou-In ahi ti heloubeh nahiu ham? Nangho nangho chang tuma nahi pouve.\x + \xo 6:19 \xt 1 Crth 3:16; 2 Crth 6:16\x*  
\v 20 Ajeh iham itileh Pathen'in nangho man tampi apeh a na chohdoh sau ahitai. Hiti ahijeh hin nang hon natahsau Pathen jabolnan peuvin.   
\c 7  
\s1 Kichenna danho  
\p
\v 1 Tun na lekhathot uva neihin thudoh u thudol'a, henge, jonthanhoiya kon'a kikangse hi thilpha ahi.  
\v 2 Hinlah hitilom'a jonthanhoina ahat tah jeh hin, pasal in ama amaji kinei cheh henlang, chule numeiyin jong ama ama pasal ji'n nei cheh uhen.  
\v 3 Jipa chun ajinun pasal'a ngaichat anei chu bulhit peh hen, chule jinu jong chun numeiya ajipa lung ngaichat chu bulhit peh hen.  
\v 4 Ajinu chun atahsa chunga thuneina chu ajipa pehen, chule ajipa jong chun ajinu chu atahsa chunga thuneina chu pehen.  
\v 5 Nangho naniuva kigel lhahna nanei uva, nupa hina a kitimat louva uma taona'a kipeh theina dinga khat le khat kingaichat tona phat chomkhat khongai ding tina ahingal louva ahileh, nupa kilung ngaichat tona jahda bol hih un. Nangho kitimlelna neijeh a Satan in na lheplhah louna ding uva chomkhat jouleh nahung umkhom kittheina dingu kati ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche kasei hi gelkhoh pehna jeh a bou ahin, thupeh kapeh nahi pouve.  
\v 7 Hinlah amichang cheh hi kei tobangin achangin um cheh leu kati. Hinla amichang cheh hi Pathen a kon thilpeh chang cheh a ahin, khat ahilouleh achom changa ahiuve.  
\v 8 Hitia hi keiman jineilou laiho le meithai ho jah a kasei ahi-keima tobanga jinei louva um hi phajoa ahi.  
\v 9 Hinlah amaho tah akitim joulou diuva ahileh jineijo dingu ahi. Angaicha gunset a um sanga jinei chu phajoa ahitai.   
\s1 Kichenna kigahna tuhchah in  
\p
\v 10 Ahin ajineisaho dingin, keiman thupeh keiya konna hilou Pakaiya konna thupeh chu kaneiye: Jinu khat chun ajipa adalhah louding ahiye.\x + \xo 7:10 \xt Matt 5:32; 19:9; Mk 10:11,12; Lk 16:18\x*  
\v 11 Hinlah aman ajipa chu adalhah tah a ahileh, amanu chu achangin umjeng hen ahilouleh amapa chuto kihoucham kit hen. Chule ajipa chun ajinu adalhah louding ahi.  
\v 12 Tun nangho adang chengse henga Pakaiya kon hilouvin keiman nakom uva hinsei inge. Christian pasal khat in atahsanlou numei khat ji a aneiya chule amanu chu aumden a achenkhompi noma ahileh, apasal chun ajinu chu adalhah louding ahi.  
\v 13 Chule Christian numei khat chun jipa atahsanlou neihen lang chule amapa chun ajinu chu umdenpi nom taleh, amanu chun apasal chu adalhah louding ahi.  
\v 14 Ajeh chu Christian jinua pang chun ajineina chu atheng ahisah ahitai, chule Christian jipa a pang chun ajineina chu atheng ahisah ahitai. Chutilou hileh nachateu chu thenglou diu ahin, hinla tun amaho atheng uve.  
\v 15 (Hinlah jipa ahilouleh jinu chu atahsanlou ahia adalhah teitei got leh sol jengin. Hitobang thua hin, Christian ajipa ahilouleh ajinu hijongleh khat joh chunga amopo tapoi, ajeh chu Pathen'in lungmonga khosa dinga nakouvu ahi).  
\v 16 Numei hon nageldoh diu chu nangho jal'a najipa teu chu huhhing'a naumsah dingu, chule pasal hon jong nangho jal'a najiteu chu huhhing'a naum sah diu ahi geldoh un.   
\ms1 Nakikou bangun um'un  
\p
\v 17 Nangho khat cheh hi Pakaiyin nakoi nau bangtah a naum dingu ahi, chule Pathen'in nakouna masah a chun um cheh un. Hiche hi houbung jouse henga ka dan sempeh ahiye.  
\v 18 Avetsahnan, mikhat chu atahsan masanga chep kitan chu akalea hei ding ahideh poi. Chule mikhat chu atahsan pet a chep kitanlou ahile tununga chep atan ngailou ahi.  
\v 19 Ajeh chu mikhat chu cheptan hen, tan hih jongleh hiche hin ima ajatchom sahna aumpoi. Athupi pen chu Pathen Thupeh ho jui hi ahi.  
\v 20 Ahimongin, nangho khat cheh hi Pathen'in nakoupet uva nahi nauva chu naum dingu ahi.  
\v 21 Nangho soh a um nahiuvem? Hichun nalung himosah dauhen, hinlah nang hon ontholna ding phat kijen naneiyuleh, hichu kilah un.  
\v 22 Chule geldoh un, Pakaiyin nakou pet uva chu soh a um nahiu leh, tua hi Pakaiya chamlhat nahiu ahitai. Chule Pakaiyin nakou pet uva chu chamlhat nahiu leh tua hi Christa a soh nahiu ahitai.  
\v 23 Pathen'in nangho dia aman tampi apeh ahitai, hijeh chun vannoiyin soh nachan sah dauhen.  
\v 24 Sopite nangho khat cheh hi Pathen'in nakou masah pet uva nahi nauva chu naum cheh dingu ahi.   
\s1 Jineilou ho leh meithai ho ding  
\p
\v 25 Tun numei khangdong jinei loulai ho thua neidoh u hi, amaho dingin Pakaiya kon'in thupeh kamupoi. Hinla Pakaiyin ami lungsetna a tahsan theiya kilom chihna chu eipen, chule hiche hi nangho toh chan kanei khompi ding nahiuve.  
\v 26 Tupet hahsatna jal'a hi, nahina bang uva naum dingu phapen in kagel'e.  
\v 27 Nangman jinu nanei leh kikhenpi ding lunggel neihih in. Jinei loulaiya naum leh, jinei tei dingin hol hih in.  
\v 28 Hinlah nangin ji chu naneiya ahileh, hichu chonset ahipoi. Chule numei khangdong chun ji aneiya ahileh, hichu chonse ahipoi. Hijeng jongleh, tuphat a hi jineiho chun boina ato dingu ahi, chule keiman hiche boina thua hi ka ontholsah got nahiuve.  
\v 29 Tun sopi te ho, hiche hi kahinsei nome: Phat um nalai hi achom behseh e. Hijeh hin, jinei pasal hon ajineiyu hi akisahboi nau pipen hisah dauhen.  
\v 30 Akap ho ahilouleh akipah ho ahilouleh thilcho ho chu akanao ahilouleh akipanau ahilouleh athil neiyuva kipum phumlut dauhen.  
\v 31 Vannoi thil mangcha ho chu, chehoa chun kipum ngaplhah dauhen. Ajeh iham itileh hiche vannoi thil ho hi ihetma bang uva, hung mangthah ding ahiye.  
\v 32 Keiman hiche hinkho gelkhohna a konna hi na onthol dingu kadei ahi. Jineilou pasal chun aphat le alunggel chu Pakai iti lunglhaiya, ana iti atoh ding angaito ahi.  
\v 33 Hinlah jinei pasal chun leiset a amopohnaho iti asuh bulhit a chule ajinu iti alunglhai ding ham ti agel ahi.  
\v 34 Alunglutna kihomkhen'a ahitai. Hitobangma a chu jinei talou numei ahilouleh jinei khalou nu chu Pakaiya kipedoh a atahsa le alhagao thengsel'a akoi thei ahi. Hinla jineisa numei chu leiset lamdol'a amopohna agelkhoh a chule ajipa alunglhai got ding ahi.  
\v 35 Hiche kasei hi na phatchomna dingu kati ahin, nangho imacha a jahdana kaneina aumpoi.  
\v 36 Hinlah pasal khat in numei khat kichenpi dinga akiteppia alam louva bola akigela chule atahsa lung ngaichat in athujo beh tah a ahileh, aman agon bangin kichenpi jenghen. Hichu chonset ahipoi.  
\v 37 Hinlah ama dettah a apan'a jineilou dinga akigel lhah a chule jineina dinga kinona aumdeh louva, chule ama kitim jou dinga akigela ahileh, jinei louva aum nahlai chu apha ahi.  
\v 38 Hiti chun ajihol kichenpia chun thilpha abol ahi, chule ajinei pailou chun abol phat cheh ahije.  
\v 39 Jinu chu ajipa hin laisea ajipa thunoiya uma ahi. Ahin ajipa athia ahileh, aman akichenpi nom nomto kicheng thei ahi, hinla hichu Pakai ngailutna jal hi ding ahi.  
\v 40 Hinlah ama dinga jinei louva aum chu phajo ding ahi, chule keiman hiche thu kahin sei hi Pathen Lhagao thumop a konna seiyin kakigelin ahi.   
\c 8  
\s1 Nasunggil in se leh pha hetna thu ngaiyin  
\p
\v 1 Tun milim houna a kikatdoh anneh thudol seikhom ute. Nanghon nahet nau chamkimtah chu mijousen na pompeh diuvin nagel'uve. Hinla hetna hin eiho kihithei sahna eipeh laiyun, ngailutna joh hin Houbung asahdoh ahi bouve.  
\v 2 Ijakai donbutna hea kingaitoa chun hetna tahbeh aneilou ahi.  
\v 3 Hinlah Pathen ngailu mi chu Pathen'in ahetpeh mi hi ahi.  
\v 4 Hiti chu ahileh, milim houna a kikatdoh saneh thu hi itin tem? Aphai, eiho jousen milim hi pathen tahbeh ahipoi, chule Pathen khat seh bou aum'e ti iheuve.  
\v 5 Van sunga le lei chunga pathen ho tia kou thei ding uminte, chule mi phabep hon pathen tampi le pakai tampi hou tahbeh uvinte.  
\v 6 Hinlah eihon Pa chu Pathen khat seh, ijakai sempa ahin, chule eiho Ama dinga hinga ihiuve ti iheuve. Chule Pakai khat seh bou Jesu Christa chu ahin, Ama jal'a Pathen'in ijakai asema chule Ama jal'a eiho hinna eipeh u ahi.  
\v 7 Ahinlah atahsan jousen che hi ahet sohkeiyu ahipoi. Mi phabep chun limsemthu pathen chu atahbeh a angaito uva, hitia chu limsemthu pathena lhatdohsa thil chu aneh tengu leh, pathen tahbeh hou dan'a kigel jiu ahi, chule se le pha ahetkhen nau chu asuboiyin ahi.  
\v 8 Eihon ithilneh u chun, Pathen lunglhaina sodohsah ponte, ti hi adih e ti iheuve. Hichu ineh louva ahileh ima imansah u aumpon, chule ineh ujongleh ima aphachom imu pouve.  
\v 9 Hinlah eiho ikichih theina dingu chu, eiho ichamlhat nau chun ase le apha hetna lhasam khat in kipalna a anei khah louna ding hi ahi.  
\v 10 Ajeh iham itileh midangin nangman hetna sangjo nanei jeh a milim houna in'a naneh chu hung muhen lang hileh, hichun amaho se le pha hetna aneiyu chu anahsahmo bola, milim houna a lhatdoh anneh chu aneh tahlou dingu ham?  
\v 11 Hitia chu nangman hetna chungnungjo nanei jeh a, Christian alhasam khat, ajeh a Christa thi, chu na suhmang ding ahitai.  
\v 12 Chule nangman atahsan midang chun adihpoi, tia alung uva atahsan uchu abol ding uva na tilkhouva ahileh, nangma Christa dounaa chonsea nahitai.  
\v 13 Hitia hi keiman ipi ham chu kaneh jeh a atahsan midangin chonsetnaa anei leh, keiman kahin laisen sa kiti neponge, ajeh chu keiman atahsan midang khat chu kakipalsah nompon ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Vetjui dinga eima ima louva kikoi  
\p
\v 1 Keima midang ho tobanga ongthol hilouva kahim? Keima solchah hilouva kahim? I-Pakaiyu Jesu chu keiman kamit tah a mulouva kahim? Keima natohnaa konna nangho Pakaiya hung hia nahi lou uham?  
\v 2 Midangin solchah a eigel louva ahijongleh nangho ding beh a kahi ahi. Keima hi Pakai solchah kahi aphot chenna nangho nahiuve.  
\v 3 Ka thuneina chung chang thua eidongho kadonbutna hiche hi ahi.  
\v 4 Keiho na in uva kachen uva chule na anneh nauva an kaneh mona diu ipi umem?  
\v 5 Solchah dang ho tobanga, Pakai sopi te ho le Peter in abol tobang uva Christian numei ji a kakipui mona diu ipi umem?  
\v 6 Ahilouleh Barnabas le keima bou hin kakihinso lhkonna dinga na katoh lhon ngaiya ham?  
\v 7 Ipi sepaiyin ama manchah ding akilotho ngaiyem? Lengpilei bola pang koipen'in alengpiga phabep jong neh theina ding thanei louva koi umem? Kelngoi hon chinga panga akelngoi phabep neh ding jong kiphal pehlou koi umem?  
\v 8 Chule hiche hi mihem ngaidan kiphongdoh maimai ahipoi. Pathen Dan in jong hitia chu asei hilou ham?  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Mose Dan in aseiye, “Bongchal'in chang achilpet tah a chu anehthei louna dinga amuh nasom louding ahi” ati. Pathen'in hiche thu aseipet a chu bongchal ding bou agelkhoh a nagel ham?\x + \xo 9:9 \xt Danbu Ni Na 25:4; 1 Tim 5:18\x*  
\v 10 Aman eiho kom'a tahbeh a thu aseina hilou ham? Henge, eiho dinga kijih a ahi, hitia chu alou khoiya panga le chang chil'a panga chun, anigel lhona chang ki-atna a chu chan anei lhon ding kinem'a ahi.  
\v 11 Kei hon Lhagao muchi nalah uva kahungtu u ahitah jeh chun, tahsalam dola neh le don thua aga kalo mona dingu umem?\x + \xo 9:11 \xt Rm 15:27\x*  
\v 12 Nangho henga thu seiphong ho na kithopi uva ahileh, amaho sanga chu keihon kithopina lenjo kamu diu hilou ham? Hinla keihon hiche chan ding chu kamangcha khapouve. Christa Kipana Thupha daltan'a aum louna ding phot ahileh ipi hijongleh kapedoh jo uve.  
\v 13 Hou-In'a natong ho khun Hou-In sunga hung kitohdoh hoa konna neh akimu jiu ahi geldohlou nahiuvem? Chule maichama natoh neiho khun maichama kipedoh thilto hoa khu chan aneiyu ahi.\x + \xo 9:13 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:1\x*  
\v 14 Hitobangma a chu, Kipana Thupha lhangsam ho chu aphatchompi hoa konna kithopina amu dingu ahi.\x + \xo 9:14 \xt Matt 10:10; Lk 10:7\x*  
\v 15 Ahijeng vang'in keiman hitiho thaneina hi khatcha kamang chapoi. Chule keiman hiche kajih hi tu apat in keiman mangcha tange tia lunggon neiya kahipoi. Ahimongin, manbeiya thuseiphongna a kakiskonna kathuneina hi abei sangin, thi ding joh kanom'e.  
\v 16 Ahijeng vang'in Kipana Thupha seiphonga pan hi kiletsahpi thei ahipoi: Pathen'in hiche hi kabol dinga kacham louva eisolna ahi. Kipana Thupha seiphong louva kaum ding chu keima dinga iti tijat um hitam?  
\v 17 Keiman hiche hi ka kihambolna a konna kabol ahileh, kalo ding lom mu ding kahi. Hinla keiman kilhen ding dan kahepoi, ajeh iham itileh Pathen'in hiche guhthim ngansena hi eipeh ahije.  
\v 18 Ahileh ipi ham kalo doh ding chu? Keiman koima imacha ngeh louva Kipana Thupha lhangsapna chanpha kachan hi hiya ahi. Hiti ahijeh a hi keiman kachan dinga lom jong ngeh louva Kipana Thupha kaseiphong ahi.   
\s1 Mijouse jen  
\p
\v 19 Keima hi chamlhatna chang koima noiya um hilou kahi jeng vangin, mi tampi Christaa kapuilut theina dinga mijouse soh a kapan ahi.  
\v 20 Keima Judah te toh kaum khom pet in, Judah te chu Christa a kapuilut theina dingin, Judah te tobangin danthu noiya hinkho kamangin ahi.  
\v 21 Keima chidang namdang ho, Judah mite chonna juilou hotoh kaumkhom tengleh, keima tah jong chuche dan'a chu hing talouva kaum hi keiman amaho chu Christa a kapuilut theina ding kati ahi. Ahin keima Pathen Danthu chu nahsahmoa kahipoi: Keiman Christa Danthu chu kajuiye.  
\v 22 Keima milhasam ho toh kaum khomna a, keiman amaho lhahsamna chu chan kanei khompi ji e, ajeh chu keiman milhachom chu Christa a kapuilut nomin ahi. Henge, keiman mitin toh thakhat hina ding kahol leh, kajo chana phabep ka huhhing jou teina dinga kati ahi.  
\v 23 Keiman kabol chasun hi Kipana Thupha the chan sohna ding kati ahi chule aphattheina kahop doh nom ahi.   
\s1 Lallukhuh sanna dia lhai  
\p
\v 24 Kilhaitetna a khu mitin lhaijia ahi, hinla mi khat in bou kipaman asan ahi. Hiti chun, jona dingin lhaiyun.  
\v 25 Golseh a jao ho khu akithem chuh nauva phatah a kithununna nei ahiuve. Amaho chun akem mangthei kipaman lona a abolu ahin, hinla eihon akem mang theilou ilojoh u ahi.  
\v 26 Hijeh a chu keima ka kalskonna chan a hi doi neiya lhai kahin, ale chum'a kahipoi.  
\v 27 Keiman golseh a lhaipa banga kabol ding dol kabol doh jou theina dinga katahsa hi kathunun ahi. Achuti louleh, midang kom'a thu kasei phong jouva keima tah alhinglou kahi khah ding ahi.   
\c 10  
\s1 Thulhun Lui vetkahna  
\p
\v 1 Kasopi te ho, nang hon masangpeh a gamthip a ipu ipateu anaum'u thudol chu nasuhmil dingu kanompoi. Amaho jouse chu achung uva um meibolin apuiyun, chule abonchauvin Twipisan chu tolgolai jot in ajot jeng uve.\x + \xo 10:1 \xt Potdohbu 13:21,22; \xt Potdohbu 14:22-29\x*  
\v 2 Mose nungjui ahijal uvin meibol sunga le twipi sunga chun abonun baptize achangun ahi.  
\v 3 Amaho jouse chun lhagao an thakhat chu ane cheh uvin,\x + \xo 10:3 \xt Potdohbu 16:35\x*  
\v 4 Chule amaho jouse chun Lhagao twi khatma chu adon khomun ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon akilhonpiu Lhagao songpima a kipat a chu adonu ahin, chule hiche songpi chu Christa ahi.\x + \xo 10:4 \xt Potdohbu 17:6; Minbu 20:11\x*  
\v 5 Hijongleh Pathen chu amaho atamjo chunga alunglhai pon, chule atahsau chu gamthip ah athethang peh in ahi.\x + \xo 10:5 \xt Minbu 14:29,30\x*  
\v 6 Hichengse ana sodoh hi eiho dinga kichih theina ding ahi, hiche hi amaho tobanga thilse ngaichatna inei louna dingu ahije.\x + \xo 10:6 \xt Minbu 11:4\x*  
\v 7 Ahilouleh amaho lah a milim hou aum bang uva ium louna dingu ahi. Pathen Thubun asei dungjuijin, “Mipiho chun kivahva na golnop anneh le don abol'un, chule amaho chu milim houna a kipah in, akipah thanomun ahi.”\x + \xo 10:7 \xt Potdohbu 32:6\x*  
\v 8 Amaho phabep chun jonthanhoi abol jeh uva mi sang somni le sangthum chu nikhat a athilo tobangu chun jonthanhoi bolpou hite.\x + \xo 10:8 \xt Minbu 25:1-18\x*  
\v 9 Ahilou jongleh Christa chu patep pou hite, amaho lah a phabep in achutibol uvin chule gul in achulih uvin ahi.\x + \xo 10:9 \xt Minbu 21:5,6\x*  
\v 10 Chule phunset bolpou hite, alah uva phabep aphunset jeh uvin, mithat vantil in amaho chu asuhmang lo'uvin ahi.\x + \xo 10:10 \xt Minbu 16:41-49\x*  
\v 11 Hichengse achung uva ana sodoh chu eiho dinga vetsahna a soh a ahi. Amaho thudol kisun hi eiho khang kichai kom'a ho kichih theina dinga ahi.  
\v 12 Nangma adingdet a nakigel a ahileh, nalhuh louna dingin ching theijin.  
\v 13 Na hinkhoa lhepna nato ho hi midangin atoho toh akikhehna aum dehpoi. Chule Pathen tahsan umtah ahin, nangman nadinpi joulou ding kalval chu Aman na chunga achuh ding phal ponte. Nangman lhepna chu nato tengleh, Aman nathoh jouva naki huhdohna ding lampi na gonpeh ding ahi.   
\s1 Milimsemthu houna'a kon jam un  
\p
\v 14 Hiti chun, kasopi deitahte, milim houna a kon'in jamdoh un.  
\v 15 Nangho lung geltoh thei mi nahiuve. Keiman kasei hi adih ahi tia na tahsan uva ahileh nangho kigel phauvin.  
\v 16 Eihon Pakai Anjon kibolna a khon'a phatthei chu iboh tengu leh, eihon Christa thisan a chu chan neiya ihilou uham?\x + \xo 10:16 \xt Matt 26:26-28; Mk 14:22-24; Lk 22:19,20\x*  
\v 17 Chule eiho mi tamtah ihivang uvin, eiho iboncha uva changlhah lum khat a chu nekhoma ihiuvin, hichun eiho tipum khat ihiuve ti vetsahna ahi.  
\v 18 Israel mipite chu gelun, amaho chun maicham a kikatdoh ho chu lungkhat tah a anehkhom jiu hilou ham?\x + \xo 10:18 \xt Thempu Dan 7:6\x*  
\v 19 Ipi seinom a kahi dem? Keiman milim houna a kikatdoh anneh chu ipi vetsahna ahi katina hintem? Ahilouleh milim kisem thu ho hi pathen ho ahiuve katina ham?  
\v 20 Ahipoi, hichu ahi naisaipoi. Hiche avetsahna thil kitoh ho hi lhagao boh ho kom'a kibol'a ahin, Pathen a kikatdoh ahipoi. Chule nangho lhagao boh hotoh najao kop dingu kanompoi.\x + \xo 10:20 \xt Danbu Ni Na 32:17\x*  
\v 21 Nanghon Pakai khon'a le lhagao boh ho khon'a chu nadon thei dehlou dingu ahi. Pakai dokhang le lhagao boh dokhanga nanehkop thei dehlou dingu ahi.  
\v 22 Pakai chu thangthip sahna ikondohsah u hingap a ham? Ama sanga ihat joh uva nagelu hitam?\x + \xo 10:22 \xt Danbu Ni Na 32:21\x*   
\s1 Ima jouse Pathen loupina ding  
\p
\v 23 Nangin “Keiman ipi hijongleh kabol ding phal ahi” nati, hinla ijakai nangma dinga phatchomna ahipoi. Nangin, “Ipi hijongleh kabol dia phatsah ahi” nati, hinla ima jouse aphachoma ahidehpoi.\x + \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Crth 6:12\x*  
\v 24 Nangma ding seh a phatna ding chu gelkhoh hih in, hinla midang phatna ding gelkhoh un.  
\v 25 Hitia chu se le pha hetna a thudoh bol louvin kailhanga sa kijoh tapou khu naneh thei ahi.  
\v 26 Ajeh iham itileh leiset hi Pakaiya ahin, chule asunga um jouse jong hi Ama a ahi.\x + \xo 10:26 \xt Labu 24:1\x*  
\v 27 Atahsan lou koi ham khat in in'a nilhah an nedinga nakouva ahileh temna namu chu nanop a ahileh sanpeh jengin. Na angsunga aluichan chu se le pha hetna thua ima dohna neilouvin sa chu nejengin.  
\v 28 (Hinlah khat touvin, hiche sa hi milim houna'a kikatdoh a ahitai, atia ahileh na seipehpa se le pha hetna jal jeh chun neh din gellhahna nei hih in).  
\v 29 Mi koiham khat in agel ding jeh man a chu kachamlhatna imalou soh ding ham?  
\v 30 Keiman anneh jeh a chu Pathen ka thangvah theiya chule hichu kanopsahpia ahileh, ipi jeh a anneh mana keima eiki oimo ding ham?  
\v 31 Hijeh chun nang hon naneh u hihen nadon'u hijongleh, ahilouleh ipi nabol'u hijongleh, abonchan Pathen loupina dingin bol'un.  
\v 32 Judah mite hihen lang, ahilouleh chidang namdang ho hijongleh, ahilouleh Pathen houbung hijongleh lungthoi sah hih un.  
\v 33 Kei jengin jong kabollam jousea hi mitin lunglhaisahna ding kabol ahi. Keima dinga aphat pen mana kabol ahipoi, mitampi huhhing'a aum theina dinga midang dinga aphapen chu kabol joh ahi.   
\c 11  
\p
\v 1 Chule keima Christa dungsun kahi bangin, nangho jong keima dungsun hiuvin.\x + \xo 11:1 \xt 1 Crth 4:16; Philp 3:17\x*   
\ms1 Pon lukhu  
\p
\v 2 Nanghon nalung uvah keima neigel jingun, chule naheng uva ka thuhil u thu chu najuiyuve, ti kahet hin keima kakipah lheh in ahi.  
\v 3 Hinlah nang hon thil khat nahet dingu keiman kadei chu: Pasal chu Christa lama mopoa ahin, numei chu ajipa henga mopoa ahi, chule Christa chu Pathen henga mopoa ahi.  
\v 4 Pasal in ataopet ahilouleh lhagao thu aseipet a alu akhua ahileh Christa ajalou ahi.  
\v 5 Hinlah numeiyin alu khu louva ataova, ahilouleh Lhagao thu aseidoh a ahileh ajipa chu ajalou ahin, hijeh a chu hiche hi alu kivoutol tobang ahitai.  
\v 6 Ahin amanu hin alu pon'a akhukhum nom louleh, aman asam jouse atan lhah ding dol ahitai! Ahin numei dinga asam tan lhah ahilouleh asam vomui chu jachat um ahijeh a, amanu chun ponlu khu chu akiken ding ahi.  
\v 7 Pasal in Pathen ahoupet a alua ima akoilou ding ahi, ajeh chu pasal chu Pathen lima kisema chule Pathen loupina sulanga ahi. Chule numeiyin Pasal loupina asuhlang hiya ahi.\x + \xo 11:7 \xt `\xt Semtilbu 1:26,27\x*  
\v 8 Ajeh iham itileh mimasa chu numeiya konna ahipon, hinla numei masa chu pasala kon ahi.\x + \xo 11:8 \xt Semtilbu 2:18-23\x*  
\v 9 Chule pasal chu numei dinga kisema ahipon, ahin numei chu pasal dinga kisema ahi.  
\v 10 Hijeh a chu numeiyin thuneina noiya um kahi ti vetsahna a, alua ponkhu akivon ding ahi, ajeh chu vantil ten avet jingu ahi.  
\v 11 Hinlah Pakai mite lah a, numeiho chu pasala konna chamlhat ahilou tobangin, pasal ho jong numeiya konna chamlhat ahi pouve.  
\v 12 Ajeh iham itileh numei masa chu pasala konna hung uma ahijeng vang'in, pasal dang khat khat cheh hi numei khat a konna hung peng doh a ahi cheh uve.  
\v 13 Nangho cheh dingin thu kitanun. Numei hin alu pon kikhu louva mipi lah a Pathen henga atao ding chu dih a hinam?  
\v 14 Pasal in sam asaova aput ding chu ama dinga kilom louva hilou ham?  
\v 15 Chule numei dinga asamsao hi akiletsahpi le athanoppi hilou ham? Ajeh chu hichu amanu dinga khukhum dinga kipea ahi.  
\v 16 Hinlah hiche thudol'a hi khattou anelkal nom aum leh, eihon hiche tailou hi chonna ding dang inei pouve, chule Pathen houbung dang hon jong anei deh pouve, ti hi kaseidoh nom ahi.   
\s1 Pakai Anjon'a umchan  
\p
\v 17 Ahivangin tun anoiya kithuhilna hoa hin, nangho ka pahcha thei pouve. Ajeh chu nangho nakimuto tengu leh thilpha sanga aphalou ding joh boldoh a hileu chun akilouve.  
\v 18 Amasan, houbunga nakikhop khom tengu leh nalah uva kibung khenna aum'e tithu kajan, chule hichu ichan hamin katahsanin ahi.  
\v 19 Hinlah, ahinai, nalah uva kibung khenna soh mong ding ahinai chutia chu nangho adih a umho hetdoh a na umna ding uva ahi!  
\v 20 Nangho naki khop khom tengu leh, nangho Pakai Anjkonna'ah na lunglut tahtah pouve.  
\v 21 Ajeh iham itileh nalah uva mi phabep chu midang to nehkhom ding golouvin nangma an cheh nakineh pai jeng uve. Hiti chun, abang khat gilkel in aum un, adang phabep akhamji tauve.  
\v 22 Ipi ham? Nehna le dkonna dinga nangma nangma in cheh neiya nahi lou uham? Ahilouleh nang hon Pathen houbung chu imacha hilou sosah ding goa chule avaichaho jachatsah goa nahiuvem? Keiman ipi kasei ding hitam? Nangho ka pachat diu nanop uvem? Hichung chang thua hin napahcha hih uvinge!   
\s1 Pakai Anjon kiphudoh  
\p
\v 23 Ajeh chu, Pakai Ama tah a konna kalahson chu nangho kapehson kit nahiuve. Pakai chu mat dinga pehdoh a aum jan chun, Pakai chun changlhah phabep ala in,  
\v 24 Hiche a chun Pathen athangvah in ahi. Chuphat in Aman ahehbal bal'in chuin aseiyin, “Hiche hi nangho dinga kipedoh katahsa ahi. Keima neigeldoh jingna dingun hiche hi bol'un,” ati.  
\v 25 Hitobangma chun an aneh jouvun, Aman khon'a lengpitwi chu ala in, aseiyin, “Hiche khon hi Pathen le Amite kitepna thah ahi–kathisan a kitepna suhdetna chu ahi. Hiche hi nadon laiseuvin keima geldohna in bol'un” ati.\x + \xo 11:25 \xt Potdohbu 24:8; Jeremiah 31:31-34; \xt Potdohbu 24:6-8\x*  
\v 26 Ajeh chu nang hon hiche changlhah hi naneh chanseuva chule hiche khon'a hi nadonlai chanseuva nang hon Pakai thina chu ahung kahsea na phondoh u ahi.   
\s1 Nangma cheh kikhol un  
\p
\v 27 Hiti chun, koi hijongleh lomlouhel'a hiche changlhah chu nea, ahilouleh hiche Pakai khon'a chu don'ah aum leh Pakai tahsa le thisana chu themmo chang ding ahi.  
\v 28 Hiche jeh a chu changlhah chu naneh masang ule khon'a chu nadon masang uva nangma tah kivetchilna nanei dingu ahiye.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu Christa tahsa chu naneh masangu, ahilouleh nadon masang uva Christa tahsa chu najabol louva ahileh, naneh le nadon a chu Pathen thutanna nangma chung tah a nakilhut hiya ahi.  
\v 30 Hiche jeh a chu nangho mi tamtah thalhoma chule naa chule phabepset jong thia nahi tauve.  
\v 31 Hinlah eimaho tah kikholtoh a hileuhen, Pathen'in hitia hi ichung uva thutanna anei louding ahi.  
\v 32 Amavang Pakaiyin ithu u atan'a thununna noiya eikoiyu tengleh, vannoi toh themmo ichantha lou diu ahi.  
\v 33 Hiti chun kasopi te, nang hon Pakai Jan Anjon bol dinga nakikhop ji tengu leh, khat le khat kingahto uvin.  
\v 34 Agilkel tahbeh monga nahiu leh, in'ah kineh jengun, chuti henlang hileh nakikhop khom tengu leh nangma chunga thutanna chu nakiloilut louding ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Lhagao thilpeh ho  
\p
\v 1 Tun, sopi deitahte, Lhagaovin thilbol theina jatchom beh eipeh nau chung chang thua neihin dohnau thudol hi, nang hon nahet khel dingu keima kanompoi.  
\v 2 Nanghon Pathen nahet masangu chun, nangho hi lhagaova lamvaiya chule paotheilou limsemthu houna a puimanga um nahi tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Hiti thua hi nang hon nahet dingu kadei chu, koima Pathen Lhagaova konna thusei chun Jesu gaosap pontin, chule Lhagao Theng panna louvin Jesu chu Pakai tithei ponte.  
\v 4 Lhagao thilpeh jat chom chom uma ahin, hinla Lhagao khat a chu lhagao thilpeh jouse aboncha hung kipan ahi.\x + \xo 12:4 \xt Rm 12:6-8\x*  
\v 5 Lhacha natohna jatchom chom aumin, hinla eihon Pakai khatma kin chu ibolu ahi.  
\v 6 Pathen'in jatchom chomin na atongin, hinla Pathen khatma chun eiho iboncha uva sunga na atongin ahi.  
\v 7 Lhagao thilpeh hi eiho khat cheh eikipeuva ahin, hiche jal'a chu eiho khat le khat ikihuto theiyu ahi.  
\v 8 Lhagao chun mikhat a thumop themna apeh ahin, hiche Lhagaoma chun michom khat chu thu hetkhen themna apen ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche Lhagaoma chun michom khat tahsannaa hatna apen, chule michom dang khat chu Lhagao chun ana damlou damsah theina thilpeh apen ahi.  
\v 10 Aman mikhat chu thil kidang dang ho boltheina thaneina apein, chule achom dang khat chu Pathen thuseidohna apein ahi. Aman michom dang khat thu kiseidoh chu Pathen Lhagaova kon ahi ahilou le lhagao chom danga kon ahi phottohna apein ahi. Chukit jongleh michom dang khat chu hetlou paoho tho theina apen, chule achom dangma chu akisei chu ipiham ti ledoh theina apein ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche Lhagao Theng chu khat ahin, lhagao thilpeh jouse hompa chu ahiye. Ama bouvin itobang lhagao thilpeh chu koi chang ding ham tichu khat cheh dinga agellhuh ahi.   
\s1 Tipum khat a kipumkhat  
\p
\v 12 Mihem tahsa hin tibah tampi aneiye, hinla tibah tampi hin tipum chu ahin semdoh ahi. Chutobanga chu Christa tahsa jong uma ahi.\x + \xo 12:12 \xt Rm 12:4,5\x*  
\v 13 I-lah uva abang phabep Judah mi, phabepma chu chidang namdang ho, chule phabep chu chamlhat ahiuve. Hinla eiho jouse hi Lhagao khat a chu baptize changa ihiuvin, chule eiho jouse Lhagao khatma a chu chan neikhoma ihiuve.  
\v 14 Ahinai, tipum hin tibah jatchom chom aneiyin, tibah khat bou ahipoi.  
\v 15 Keng chun, “Keima khut kahilou jeh in keima tipum'ah kajaopoi” tileh hichun tipuma chu ahisah deh louding ahipoi.  
\v 16 Chule bilkol chun, “Keima mit kahi loujeh in keima tipuma kajaopoi,” tileh hichun tipuma ahisah deh louding ahipoi.  
\v 17 Tipum jouse chu mit hitahen lang hileh, iti kho najah ding hitam? Ahilouleh nati pumpi chu nakol khat hitaleh, ipia anam najah thei ding hitam?  
\v 18 Hinlah itahsau hin tibah tampi aneiyin, chule Pathen'in khat khat cheh hi aphatsahna mun mun'a akoi cheh ahiye.  
\v 19 Tahsa chun tibah khat seh neitahen lang hileh tipum khat chu iti datmo um hi ding hitam?  
\v 20 Ahinai, tibah tampi aumin, hinla tipum khat bou ahi.  
\v 21 Mit chun khut jah a, “Keiman nangma kangaichapoi” atithei louhel ding ahi. Luchang chun keng jah a, “Nangma kangaichapoi,” atithei louhel ahi.  
\v 22 Tahbeh in, tibah ho lah a athalhom pen le aphatchomna neibeh louva igel hou hi angai khoh pen joh ahinom jiuve.  
\v 23 Chule eihon igelkhoh beh lou u ijabol behlou hou hi eihon phatah a ivettup uva itom jiu ahiye. Hiti chun, eihon akimulou ding ho hi phate chan ivesui jiuvin ahi.  
\v 24 Ja ding dol tibah ho hi phatecha vetsui jong angai jipoi. Hitia hi Pathen'in tipum hi akoikhoma agunchelou tibah ho hi jabolbena le vetsui jepna apeh ahi.  
\v 25 Hiche hin tibahho dinga kitona ahin sodoh theina dinga, tibah jouse khat le khat kikhohsah tona ahin umdohsah theina ding uva ahi.  
\v 26 Tibah khat in athohgim a ahileh, tibah jousen hichu athohgim piuvin, chule tibah khat chun jabolna akimua ahileh, tibah jouse chun akipa huvin ahi.  
\v 27 Nangho jouse hi naboncha uva Christa tipum nahiuvin, chule nangho khat khat cheh hi hiche tibah a chu panga nahiuve.  
\v 28 Hichea hin, Pathen'in houbunga dinga tibah a alhendoh ho chu aum'e: Amasan solchah ho, abanin themgao ho, athumnan mihil ho, chubana melchihna kidang dang bol ho, adamlou damsah theina, midang panpi theina, lamkai hina lhagao thilpeh chang, hetlou pao hoa thusei theina.\x + \xo 12:28 \xt Eph 4:11\x*  
\v 29 Eiho jouse solchah ihiuvem? Eiho jouse hi themgao ihiuvem? Melchihna kidang boldoh theina inei sohkei uvam?  
\v 30 Adamlou damsah theina thilpeh ichan sohkei uvam? Paochom tho theina thilpeh nanei mong hinam? Eiho jouse hetlou pao ledoh theina thilpeh ichan sohkeiyu vem?  
\v 31 Hitia chu nang hon aphachom pen lhagao thilpeh ho chu nalung got dingu ahi. Hijongleh tun keiman mijouse dinga aphapen hinna lampi chu navetsah uvinge.   
\c 13  
\s1 Thilpeh lenpen  
\p
\v 1 Keiman leiset chunga pao jouse le vantil ho paogeiyin tho thei ingting, hinla midang ngailu louvin um taleng, keima chu sum-eng kivoging le khutbeh kibeng gin tobang bep kahi ding ahi.  
\v 2 Keiman Pathen Thu seitheina thilpeh nei ingting, chule Pathen'in aguh a athilgon ho jouse hetkhenna neiyin chule mol ho jouse tolmangsoh theina tahsan chu nei nama jonglehng, keiman midang chu kangailut louva ahileh, imacha kahilou hi ding ahi.\x + \xo 13:2 \xt Matt 17:20; 21:21; Mk 11:23\x*  
\v 3 Keiman kanei chasun chu mivaicha peingting chule kati pumpi hi pedoh leng, hichu kaki letsahpi thei ahi, hinla keiman midang chu ngailu lou hitaleng, keiman imacha phatchomna kanei louding ahi.  
\v 4 Ngailut hi athohhat in chule hepina nei ahi. Ngailut hi athangthip poi ahilouleh aham hoithopoi ahilouleh akiletsahpoi,  
\v 5 ahilouleh a-engsepoi. Ama dei bou angeh gunsetpoi. Lung himopina aneipon, chule akibol phat louna ho aching denpoi.  
\v 6 Adih louva kibol akipapi pon, hinla thutah chun ajo tengleh akipahji.  
\v 7 Ngailutna hi amoh lung lhadai jipoi, atahsanna alhadai jipoi, aphat tinin akinem jin, chule itobang hahsatna hijongleh athoh jouve.  
\v 8 Pathen thu seidohna le hetlou paoho a thuseina ho chule hetkhenna kidang dehset neina jong apanna bei ahung hiphat um ding ahi. Hinla ngailutna hi imatih chan'a um jing ding ahi!  
\v 9 Tua ihetthei nau hi alhasamin chule akimpon ahi, chule Pathen thu seidohna thilpeh geiya hi aboncha hijoulou kiphasam nalai ahije.  
\v 10 Chamkimna chu ahunglhun phat tengleh, abulhing louse hi panna beisoh ding ahitai.  
\v 11 Keima chapang kana hi chun, thusei lunggel chule ngaitona chu chapang bangin kaumin ahi. Hinla keima khangdong kahung hichun, chapang ngolna ho chu kajom tapoi.  
\v 12 Tua thil ho hi chamkim louva phatvet a kichen louva ivet u tobangbep ahin, chuphat teng vang leh ijakai thengsel'a chamkim keiya imu dingu ahitai. Tua kahet jouse hi akimpon chule abulhingpoi, chuteng vang leh ijakai chamkim keiya kahet ding ahitai, Pathen'in eihet chamkim kei tobang hi ding ahitai.  
\v 13 Thil thum hi a-itih a umden ding ahi–tahsan, kinep chule ngailut chule hiche ho lah a hin ngailut achungnung pen'e.   
\c 14  
\s1 Gao thusei le paochom tho  
\p
\v 1 Ngailut hi nalungtup sangpen'u hihen. Hintin Lhagao thilpeh thilbol theina aphadehset chu-adehset a Pathen thu seidoh theina lhagao thilpeh chu nalunga na ngaichat u hihen.  
\v 2 Ajeh chu nangman pao chomchom tho theina thilpeh chu changin lang, miho chun na thusei heta hih ule, nangma Pathen tobou kihoulima nahi ding ahitai. Nangman Lhagao thahat a thu nasei chu hinan natin, hijongleh hiche ho chu het hahsa hi ding ahitai.  
\v 3 Hinlah Pathen thu seidoh a vang chun midang ahatsah a, atilkhouva chule amaho chu alhamonsah ahi.  
\v 4 Paochom chom thoa chu ama tah kitil khouva ahin, hinla Pathen thu seidoh a chun Houbung apumpia athahatsah ahi.  
\v 5 Naboncha uva paochom chom natho theiyu hileh kati lheh in, hinla na boncha uva Pathen thu seidoh theina joh neileu chun kadeijoi. Ajeh chu Pathen thu seidoh chu houbung apumpia kitil khouna dinga pao chomchom tho sanga kiphamo joa ahi.   
\s1 Paochom tho chu ledoh ding ahi  
\p
\v 6 Kasopi deitahte ho, keima nakom uva hung ingting hetlou pao khat in thu seileng, hichu iti na phatchompi thei dingu ham? Hinla keiman thu kiphong doh a konna ahilouleh hetsahna jat chombeh a konna ahilouleh Pathen thu seidoh a konna ahilouleh thuhil'a konna na phatchomna dingu kahin pohpeh u hileh kati.  
\v 7 Tumging manchah ho: theile ahilouleh selangdah ho jeng jong hinna neilou ahivanga paocheng kicheh tah a thu kisei toh tekah thei ahiuve. Ajeh chu ahi ding banga suhging ahilouleh koima chan agin ngei chu ahetdoh theilou dingu ahi.  
\v 8 Chule sumkon mutgin akicheh louleh, sepaiho chun galsatna a dinga kikou ahiu iti ahetdoh thei dingu ham?  
\v 9 Chutobang chu ahi nangho jong, nang hon miho chu ahetlou paovin gahou leu chun, nang hon ipi naseiyu chu ama hon iti ahet dingu hitam? Mun onglaiya thusei tobang bep nahiu ahitai.  
\v 10 Vannoiya hin paojat chom chom tampi aumin, chule pao kiti hin athuko aum cheh e.  
\v 11 Hinlah keiman paokhat chu hetahih leng, thuseipa dinga chu gamdang mi kahi ding, chule thuseipa chu keima dinga gamdang mi hi ding ahitai.  
\v 12 Chule nangho dinga jong chutima chu ahi. Nangho Lhagaovin thilbol theina apeh thua hetnomna naneiyu ahin, houbung apumpia tilkhou theina ding chu hol'un.  
\v 13 Hitia chu paochom chom thoa chun akiseidoh ho chu ledoh theina dinga jong tao ding ahi.  
\v 14 Ajeh chu keima paochom chom thoa kataova ahileh, kalhagao chu atao ahinan, hinla ipi kasei chu keiman kahepoi.  
\v 15 Chuti ahileh ikatia pha ham? Keima Lhagaovin tao ingting, chule kahetna thuchenga jong tao vinge. Keiman Lhagaovin la sangting, chule kahet thei thuchenga la sang kate.  
\v 16 Ajeh chu nangman Pathen chu lhagao bouva na vahchoi ahileh, nangma nahe loubeh ho tochun Pathen chu iti navahchoi khom thei dingu ham? Nangman ipi nasei ahijong helou ho chu thangvahna a iti nangma to pangkhom thei dingu ham?  
\v 17 Nangman thangvahna chu phatah in penan nate, hinla nangma thangvahna chun miho chu thahatsahna pechom deh ponte.  
\v 18 Nangho chengse koipen sanga pao kaha tho thei joh jal jeh hin Pathen ka thangvah in ahi.  
\v 19 Hinlah houbung kikhop khomna a keiman hettheiya thucheng nga seidoh ding chu hetlou paova thucheng sangsom sei sangin kanomjoi.   
\s1 Paochom tho atahsan loute dinga melchihna  
\p
\v 20 Sopi deitahte ho, hiche ho hetkhenna a hin chapang ngol bang hih un. Aselam ahipouva ahileh khohelou chapang tobang hiuvin, hinla hetkhen themna lampang thua pilhing tah hiuvin.  
\v 21 Hiche hi Pathen Thubua akisun'e, “Keiman kamite ho jah a pao jahkhahlou ho kaman ding chule gamdang miho kamanchah ding ahi. Ahijeng vang'in, hiche jenga jong chu amaho kasei thua nunglou dingu ahi,” tin Pakaiyin aseiye.\x + \xo 14:21 \xt Isa 28:11,12\x*  
\v 22 Hitia hi nangman paochomchom tho hi atahsan ho dinga hilouva atahsan louho dinga amelchihna ahi ti nahetai. Pathen thu seidoh vang hi atahsanlou hoa ding hilouva, atahsan hoa ding ahi.  
\v 23 Hitobangma chun, hitiho hetna neilou ahilouleh atahsanlou ho hu'ah na-houbung uva hungu henlang, chule amichang cheh in hetlou paova thu kisei chu jataleu amaho chun angol uva ahitai tia agel dingu ahi.  
\v 24 Hinlah nangho jousen Pathen Thu naseiyuva, atahsan lou khat ahilouleh miho hiche ho hetna neilou nakikhop nauva hung uleh, ama hon chonsetna kigeldoh uvin tin chule nathuseiyu chun athu atan ding ahi.  
\v 25 ama hon angaiyuva ahileh, aguhthim thu uchu kilangdoh intin, chule amaho chu akhup uva dilsu uvin tin chule Pathen ahou uva, “Hikom'a nalah uva hin Pathen aum'e ati dingu ahi.”   
\s1 Houbung kikhopna a umdan  
\p
\v 26 Aphai, kasopi te ho, seichom tauhite. Nangho nakikhop khom tengu leh mi khat in la sahen, midang khat in thu hil-hen, achom dangma chun Pathen'in ahenga gotchombeh a aphondoh chu sei hen, mikhat in paochom chom tho henlang, chule michom khat in ipi kiseina ahi chu ledoh hen. Ahin akibol jouse chu nangho jouse tahsan hatsahna hihen.  
\v 27 Mini ahilouleh mithum kalvalin paoho thoda hen. Amaho chun amasan khatbou seisah uhen, chule ama hon aseiyu chu mikhat in ipi asei chu ledoh peh pai hen.  
\v 28 Hinlah koima alethei aum louva ahileh, amaho chu nakikhop nauva chun thipbeh in touvu hen, chule achang uvin Pathen kom'a seijo uhen.  
\v 29 Mini ahilouleh mi thum'in gaothu seiyuhen, chule midangsen akiseidoh cheng chu datkhenna neiyuhen.  
\v 30 Ahin koiham khat in Pathen thu aseiya chule michom dang khat in Pakaiya konna thuphondoh amu leh, thuseipa chu thip jeng hen.  
\v 31 Hitia hi Pathen thusei hon thuseina phat banneicha anei cheh dingu, hitia hi amichang cheh in hetna anei dingu chule kitilkhou ding ahi tauve.  
\v 32 Pathen thusei chun alhagaovu kithunun theina aneiyun, chule ama phat akinga thei diu ahiye.  
\v 33 Ajeh chu Pathen hi akisunohphah thei Pathen ahipoi hinla cham-lungmon Pathen hijoa ahi, Pathen mitheng te ho kikhop khomna jouse ngai bangin.  
\v 34 Numeiho hi houbung kaikhomna a thipbeh ding ahiuve. Amaho dingin thusei chu alompoi. Amaho thunoiya um dingu, chonna danin asei tobang hidiu ahi.  
\v 35 Ama hon thudoh nom aneiyuva ahileh ajipateu inmun'a akidoh dingu ahi, ajeh chu numei ho dinga houbung kikhop khomna a thusei chu umdan dihlou ahi.  
\v 36 Ahilouleh Pathen thu hi nangho Corinth mite ho a pat a hung kipan'ah ahi tia ngaitoa nahiuvem? Nangho kom bouva thu hi kipedoh a nangaitou ham?  
\v 37 Nangho themgaova nakigel uva ahilouleh lhagao mia kigel nahiuleh, keiman nangho ka seipeh hi Pakai Ama tah a konna thupeh ahi.  
\v 38 Hinlah nang hon hiche hi na hetdohlou uva ahileh, nangho tah jong hetdoh nahilou dingu ahi.  
\v 39 Hiti hin, kasopi deitahte ho, Pathen thusei nomna neiyun, chule paochom chom tho jong jada hih un.  
\v 40 Hinlah imalam jouseah kitup tah le kisuhsela bola hiuvin.   
\c 15  
\s1 Thoudoh Christa, tahsan photchetna  
\p
\v 1 Kasopi deitahte, tumasanga naheng uva Kipana Thupha kahung lhangsap thu chu keiman nahin geldoh sahkit uvinge. Chupet chun nasang uvin chule tugeiyin nading det jing nauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Keiman najah uva ka seipeh u thu chu na tahsan jom jing uva ahileh hiche Kipana Thupha chun nahuhhingu ahi–apat a pat a adihlou thu chu tahsana nahilou pouva ahileh.  
\v 3 Keiman naheng uva akhohpen tah keima henga ana kipe chu kahin pehson nahiuve–Christa chu Pathen Thubun asei dungjuijin ichonset jal'un athin ahi.\x + \xo 15:3 \xt Isa 53:5-12\x*  
\v 4 Ama chu akivuiyin, chule Pathen Thubun asei dungjuijin, ani-thum nin athoudohtai.\x + \xo 15:4 \xt Labu 16:8-10; Matt 12:40; Act 2:24-32\x*  
\v 5 Ama chu Peter in amun chujouvin somle ni ho chun amu uve.\x + \xo 15:5 \xt Lk 24:34; \xt Matt 28:16,17; Mk 16:14; Lk 24:36; Jn 20:19\x*  
\v 6 Chujouvin, khatveiyin anung jui mi janga val hon khatvei mun amuvin ahi, amaholah a atamjo ahing nalaiyun, hinla phabep chu athi tauve.  
\v 7 Chupet in Jacob in ama chu amun chujouvin solchah jousen amu uve.  
\v 8 Achaina keiyin, aphat louva peng bangin, keiman jong Ama chu kamun ahi.\x + \xo 15:8 \xt Act 9:3-6\x*  
\v 9 Ajeh chu keima solchah ho jouse lah a imacha hiloupen kahi. Ahimongin Pathen houbung ana gimbol hesoh a kahi jeh hin solchah ti dinga jong kiloma kahipoi.\x + \xo 15:9 \xt Act 8:3\x*  
\v 10 Hinlah tun ipi thu um jongleh kahi ahi, Pathen'in alungsetna chu kachunga asunlhah ahitah jeh hin-chule hichu phatchomna bei ahidehpoi. Ajeh chu keiman solchah dang ho sangin na kaha tohgimjon, hinla hichu keijoh hita louva Pathen'in alungsetnaa keiya na atoh ahijo bouve.  
\v 11 Hiti chun keiman seiphong teng ahilouleh ama hon ka thusei ma tahsanna nakisanu thudol seiphong kit jonglehu ima chom aumpoi, ajeh chu keihon kabon chauva na tahsan u thudol chu kasei phong khomu ahi.   
\s1 Christa thodoh, ikinepnau  
\p
\v 12 Hinlah hiche hi nei seipeh un-Christa chu thinaa kon'in athoutai katiu leh, itidan'a nalah uva phabep in athiho thokitna aumpoi tia nahiu ham?  
\v 13 Ajeh chu athiho thokitna aumlouva ahileh Christa jong chu kaithouva um dehlou hi ding ahitai.  
\v 14 Chule Christa chu kaithoulou anahita leh, thu kaseiphong leu hi mohseh hita ding, chule na tahsan 'u jong chu mohseh hi ding ahitai.  
\v 15 Chule solchah keiho jouse jong hi Pathen lamdola jousei kahi dingu ahitai-ajeh chu keihon Christa chu Pathen'in lhan'a kon'in akaithouve kana tiu ahi. Hinlah thokitna aumlouva ahileh hiche kisei chu dih theilou ding ahitai.  
\v 16 Chule athiho thokitna chu umlou hitaleh, Christa chu kaithou hilou ding ahitai.  
\v 17 Chule Christa chu kaithou hilou anahi khah leh, na tahsan u chu panna bei hi ding chule nangho hi na chonset nauvin themmonachanjing nahlai dingu ahiye.  
\v 18 Hiche chung chang thua hi, Christa tahsana thiho jouse chu mang thah hidiu ahitai.  
\v 19 Chule Christa itahsanu hi tuhinkhoa ding bou hita leh, vannoiya midang jouse sanga khoto umpen ihi dingu ahitai.   
\s1 Melma nunungpen suhset'a um  
\p
\v 20 Hinlah, Christa chu athiho lah a kon'in kaithou ahitah behnai. Ama athiho jouse lah a aga masapen chu ahitai.  
\v 21 Hitia hi mikhat jal'a vannoi a thina ahunglhun banga chu, athiho lah a konna thokitna hi michom khat jal'a hi ding ahi.  
\v 22 Eiho iboncha uva Adama hungkon ihijeh uva ithi sohkei dingu ahi tobanga, Christaa hiho jouse chu hinkho thah kipe ding ahi.  
\v 23 Hinlah hiche thokitna thudol'a hin akigontoh dol aum'e. Christa chu ga kiloh masapen ahi, abana Christaa thiho jouse chu Ama ahungkit tengleh kaithouva um ding ahitai.  
\v 24 Aman vaipoho le athunei ho chule athanei ho chu asuhmang soh jou tengleh, Lenggam chu Pa Pathen kom'a apehdoh a chujou tah leh achaina hung hi ding ahi.  
\v 25 Ajeh chu Christa hin Amelmate jouse chu akengto noiya akoi tokahsea vai ahom tei ding ahi.\x + \xo 15:25 \xt Labu 110:1\x*  
\v 26 Chule melma anunungpen akisumang ding chu thina ahi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu Pathen Thubun aseiyin, “Pathen'in ijakai Ama thunoiya akoi sohkei ahitai,” ati. *(Hichea, “ijakai Ama thuneina noiya akoi” kiti hin Pathen Ama akijaosah thapoi, Ama chun Christa hi Athuneina apehdoh joh ahi bouve).\x + \xo 15:27 \xt Labu 8:6\x*  
\v 28 Aman ijakai athunoiya akoi sohkei tengleh, Chapa Ama tah jong chu Pathen thunoiya kikhum lut intin, Pathen Achapa ijakai chunga thuneina pepa chu, ijakai a achungvuma imalam jousea athunei hi ding ahitai.   
\s1 Thokitna seilep ga  
\p
\v 29 Athisaho kaithouva umlou ding ahia ahileh, thi jal'a baptize chanlona ajeh ipiba hitantem? Athiho chu nikhat le kaithou ding ahilouleh ipi bol ngaiya ham?  
\v 30 Chule ipi dinga aphat phat a keiho hin kahinkhou hi hahsatna kathoh jiu hintem?  
\v 31 Ajeh chu kasopi te ho, kihahselna theijin keiman anitinin thina kakimaitopi jinge. I-Pakaiyu Christa Jesun nanghoa anatoh hi keima kakiletsahna tahbeh chu ahi.  
\v 32 Chule gamsaho toh (Ephesus khomite toh) kakidel lona ipi phatchomna hintem? Athisaho thokitna umlou ding ahia ahileh? Chule thokitna aum louva ahileh, “Eiho kivah'u hitin, donu hite, ajeh chu ajinga kithi tading chu!” itidiu ahitai.\x + \xo 15:32 \xt Isa 22:13\x*  
\v 33 Chutobanga thusei ho chu kingol bolsah hih un, ajeh chu, “kivoppi phalouvin chon chan phalou asoji,” kitia ahi.  
\v 34 Adih chu ipipen ahi geltoh uvin lang, chule chonse tahih un. Ajeh chu hiche hi naja chatna ding uva kasei doh ahi, nangho mi phabep Pathen he tahbeh lou nahiuve.   
\s1 Loupina tahsa vou  
\p
\v 35 Hinlah khat touvin, “Mithiho itobanga thoudoh dingu ham? Itobang tahsa pum anei dingu ham?” tin dongun te.  
\v 36 Itobang ngol hoi thudoh hitam! Nangman muchi tol'a natu chu athi kahsen ahung kehdoh theipoi.  
\v 37 Chule nangman leiset a nakoi chu suhlou chang mu hihen ipi pen chu natulut hita jongleh aphung ahung khang ding chu ahi hih laiye.  
\v 38 Chutengleh Pathen'in ahin hisah nom ding vouthah chu ahinpeh ding ahi. Muchi khat cheh a konna chu thingphung chom chom hung khang touva ahi.  
\v 39 Chutobangma a chu tahsa pum jong jatchom chom ahi, mihem tahsa pum le ganhingho tahsa pum, vacha ho tahsa pum, chule ajat chombeh nga tahsa pum geiya uma ahi.  
\v 40 Leiset a tipumho aum tobangin, Van'a jong tipumho aumin ahi. Van'a tahsapum loupina chu leiset a tahsapum loupina toh ajatchomin ahi.  
\v 41 Nisa hin loupina jatkhat aneiyin, lha le ahsi hon jong khat cheh hina ma anei cheh uve. Ahsiho jeng jong khat khat hi aloupinau ajatchom cheh in ahi.  
\v 42 Mithiho thokitna jong chutobangma chu ahi. Leiset a itahsau hi ithi tengu leh leinoiya iphumlut jiuvin, hinla a-itih a hingjing dinga hung thoudoh ding ahiuve.  
\v 43 Itahsau hi abong abaija kiphumlut a ahin, hinla hiche ho hi loupina a hung thoudoh ding ahiuve. Amaho hi thanei louva kivuilut ah ahin, hinla thahat a hung thoudoh ding ahiuve.  
\v 44 Amaho hi angaiya mihem vouphea kivuiya ahiuvin, hinla amaho hi lhagaolam vouphea hung thoudoh ding ahiuve. Ajeh chu angaidol'a tahsa vouphe aum tobanga chu lhagaolam dola vouphe aumin ahi.  
\v 45 Pathen Thubun, “Mimasa Adam chu hinna nei mihem ahung hi,” tin eiseipeh uvin ahi. Hinlah Adam nunungpa chu, Christa kiseina, hinna pea Lhagao ahi.\x + \xo 15:45 \xt Semtilbu 2:7\x*  
\v 46 Amasa tahsa tipumho hung um masaa chujouva lhagaova tipumho chu khonunga hung uma ahi.  
\v 47 Mimasa Adam chu leiset leivuiya konna kisema ahin, mihem aninapa Christa chu Van'a konna hung'ah ahi.  
\v 48 Leiset mite hi leiset mihem chuto akilou uvin, chule van'a mite chu van'a hungkonpa tobang ahiuve.  
\v 49 Tua hi eiho leiset a mihempa tobang chu ihiuvin, phat khat le van'a hungkonpa tobang chu ihung hi dingu ahi.   
\s1 Achaina galjona  
\p
\v 50 Kasopi deitahte ho, keiman kasei hi, itahsapheu hin Pathen Lenggam alotheipoi. Hiche thi thei tahsaphe hin tonsot a um ding gou alo theipoi.  
\v 51 Hinlah keiman thuguh kidangtah na phondoh peh uvinge. Eiho jouse iboncha uva ithi sohkei dingu hilou, hinla iboncha uva vouso kikhel ding ihiuve.\x + \xo 15:51 \xt 1 Thes 4:15-17\x*  
\v 52 Hichu phulou helouva, mitphetkah sunga sumkon nunungpen chu hung kimut ging ding ahi. Ajeh chu sumkon chu ahung kimut ging tengleh, Pakaiya ana thisaho chu vou kikhel a thoudoh diu ahi. Chule eiho ahing chengse ivouvu kikhel ding tonsot a hing ding ihitauve.  
\v 53 Ajeh chu athi ding itahsau hi thilouhel ding tahsa vouva kikhel ding, athi thei itahsau hi athi thei talou tahsa voupua kikhel ding ahitai.  
\v 54 Chuteng, athi ding tahsa ineihou hi athi talou ding tahsahoa ahung kikhel tengleh, hiche Pathen Thubu in asei, “Thina chu jonain avallhum tai”\x + \xo 15:54 \xt Isa 25:8\x*  
\v 55 “Vo thina, hoiba ham namijo na? Vo thina, hoiba ham namide na?” kiti chu guilhung ding ahi.\x + \xo 15:55 \xt Hosea 13:14\x*  
\v 56 Ajeh chu chonset hi thina a dinga midep a panga ahi, chule Danthu hin chonset thaneina apeh ahi.  
\v 57 Hinlah Pathen thangvah in umhen! Aman chonset le thina jo jou theina I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa jal'in eipeuvin ahi.  
\v 58 Hijeh chun, kasopi deitahte ho, hat un chule suhlong thei louvin pangun. Pakaiya dingin thanom tah in tong jingun, ajeh chu na thilbol u chu Pakaiya dingin phatchomna bei imacha aumpoi ti naheuve.   
\c 16  
\s1 Mithengte dia sum donkhom  
\p
\v 1 Tun Jerusalem'a Pathen mite dinga neitokhomna sum thua neihin doh nauva hin, nang hon jong Galatia gamkai pumpia houbungho henga ajui dingu kapeh chu najui ding uva katem nahiuve.\x + \xo 16:1 \xt Rm 15:25,26\x*  
\v 2 Hapta seh a ni masapenni leh, nasum kilodoh uva kon chun atatoh kham bep ana koidoh uvin. Keima kahunglhuna khatvei lah a kahung lahkhom tokah ngah hih uvin.  
\v 3 Keima kahung tengleh, na thilpeh u Jerusalem'a podinga na lhendoh hou dinga seiphatna lekhathot kajih ding ahi.  
\v 4 Chule keima dinga amaho toh lhon ding chu ahimona aum louva ahileh, keima tojong kaki lhon theiyu ahi.   
\s1 Mimal tohgon  
\p
\v 5 Keima Macedonia kache jou tengleh nangho vil dinga naheng uva kahung ding ahi, ajeh chu keima Macedonia a konna hung kholjin ding kalunggon ahi.\x + \xo 16:5 \xt Act 19:21\x*  
\v 6 Ijem itileh phat chomkhat, phalbi sunga nangho to umkhom kanomin, chujou tengleh aban kachena ding alampi nei gonpeh uva neisol theiyu ahitai.  
\v 7 Tuchunga hi nangho chomcha hungvila chule aban chebe ding ti kagongpoi. Keima kahunga Pakaiyin eiphatsah ahileh chomkhat beh um ding kanop ahi.  
\v 8 \x + \xo 16:8 \xt Act 19:8-10\x*Tutadi hin, Pentecost Kut lhunkah a dingin Ephesus khopia hin um inge.\x + \xo 16:8 \xt Thempu Dan 23:15-21; Danbu Ni Na 16:9-11\x*  
\v 9 Hikom'a natoh lentah tohna dingin kot lentah akihongin, hinla eidouva mi tamtah aumun ahi.  
\v 10 Timothy ahung tengleh, engbolna ima neihih un. Aman keima Pakai natoh katoh tobanga hi Pakai na chu atoh ahiye.\x + \xo 16:10 \xt 1 Crth 4:17\x*  
\v 11 Koiman ama hi hutum le gihna nei dauhen. Ama kaheng lama ahung kile tengleh na phatthei nau pumin hinsol un. Ama hi atahsan midangto ahung kilhon ding kakinemin ahi.  
\v 12 Tun isopiu Apollos chung changa hin–keiman ama chun atahsan sopi dang ho toh nahung vilna dingun katemin ahi, hinla tutadin ama achenom hih laiye. Aman phat kijen dom phat dang anei teng nahung vil dingu ahi.   
\s1 Achaina tilkhouna  
\p
\v 13 Kihong phauvin, Tahsanna a chun dingdet un, Lung ngam'un. Hat un.  
\v 14 Chule nabol jouseu chu ngailutna in bol'un.  
\v 15 Stephanas le a insung mite abonchauva Greece a aga masapen ahiuve ti nang hon naheuvin, chule amaho hin Pathen mite kin bolnaa ahinkhou aman jengu ahi. Kasopi deitahte ho, kangeh nahiuve,\x + \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Crth 1:16\x*  
\v 16 Amaho le midang ho kiphal theng tah le lunglut tah a natong ho thunoiya kipelut un.  
\v 17 Stephanas, Fortunetas chule Achaicus hikom mun ahungu hin eikipasah lheh jengin ahi. Nanghon hikom'a kithopina neipeh theilou u chu amaho hin eikithopiu ahi e.  
\v 18 Amaho nangho dinga kitilkhouna phatah ahibang uvin, keima dingin jong ahiuve. Hitobang loma phatah a lhacha kinbol ho jouse chu nakipapi nau navetsah tei diu dol ahi.   
\s1 Achaina lemna le salam thu  
\p
\v 19 Asia gamkai sunga hilam a houbung um hon, Aquila le Priscilla chule ain'a kikhom houbung chun Pakaiya chibai nahin bol uve.\x + \xo 16:19 \xt Act 18:2\x*  
\v 20 Sopite ho hikom'a umho jousen chibai nahin thot uve. Khat le khat Christian kingailutnan chibai kibolun.  
\v 21 HICHE HI KEIMA PAUL IN KA KHUTTAH A KAJIH KICHIBAINA THUCHENG AHI.  
\v 22 Koitobang Pakai ngailu lou auma ahileh, ama chu gaosap changa ahi. Ka Pakaiyu hungin!  
\v 23 I-Pakaiyu Jesu milungsetna chun naumpiu hen.  
\v 24 Christa Jesu a kangailutna naboncha uva chunga umhen. Amen.   